The Uk Royal family has announced that a Royal baby is on the way. Meghan Markle is expecting a baby with her husband Prince Harry. This means that the Queen Mother, Queen Elizabeth II is going to be a great-grandmother yet again. The Kensington Palace made the announcement stating that the child will be due in spring 2019. This announcement comes five months after the fairy tale wedding between Meghan Markle and Prince Harry held at Windsor Castle. Prince Harry is said to be a doting uncle to Prince Williams children and also a Godfather to children of several of his friends. Their Royal Highnesses The Duke and Duchess of Sussex are very pleased to announce that The Duchess of Sussex is expecting a baby in the Spring of 2019. pic.twitter.com/Ut9C0RagLk â€” Kensington Palace (@KensingtonRoyal) October 15, 2018 